Ranges of immediate values in SPARC assembly language instructions:

simm13 (used in arithmetic and load/store instructions):  -4096 to +4095
imm22 (used in SETHI): 0 to 4193404 (4 MB)
disp22 (used in Bicc): 4 * disp22 => - 2^23 to 2^23 - 1 (relative to pc)
disp30 (used in CALL): 4 * disp30 => - 2^31 to 2^31 - 1 (relative to pc)
